WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.310
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:04.710
Day

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:07.510
57. Well, I guess I stirred the internet

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:11.589
up a little bit with the XRP video.

00:00:11.599 --> 00:00:13.950
My heart is just to

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:16.710
help. We hear in part, we see in

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:18.950
part. That is all I can

00:00:18.950 --> 00:00:18.960
say—whenever

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:20.830
the Lord showed me the

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.550
things he has shown me, clear back in

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:25.910
2017, and I’ve been praying over silver

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:27.910
and gold. I’ve told you this stuff for a

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:31.470
long time, and all I know is I feel an

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:34.069
urgency in my spirit to warn the body of

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:36.869
Christ about

00:00:36.869 --> 00:00:36.879
what’s

00:00:36.879 --> 00:00:39.270
coming. It could be a year from

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:40.830
now, it could be six months, it could be

00:00:40.840 --> 00:00:42.750
in

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:46.229
January, but I told you about

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:49.950
the dream I had about the copper pot, and

00:00:49.950 --> 00:00:49.960
I’m

00:00:49.960 --> 00:00:52.189
going to go over that again today. I

00:00:52.199 --> 00:00:55.790
think it’s important for you to know

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.349
about the copper

00:00:57.359 --> 00:01:01.549
pot, so I hope this video blesses

00:01:01.549 --> 00:01:01.559
you.

00:01:01.559 --> 00:01:04.750
It was like a normal night; I

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:06.390
just went to sleep. It was just a

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:10.789
dream, but in this dream,

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:12.149
I was

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:14.550
standing in a

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:17.469
crowd of elderly men

00:01:17.479 --> 00:01:21.590
and women. They had gray beards

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:24.789
and gray hair. They were

00:01:24.789 --> 00:01:24.799
elderly—I’m

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:26.550
talking

00:01:26.550 --> 00:01:26.560
Moses-like

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:31.390
beards, real long beards. I

00:01:31.390 --> 00:01:31.400
don’t

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:34.149
know what symbolism means in

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:37.069
dreams; I’m not a dream interpreter, so I

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:39.710
just go by what the Holy Spirit shows me

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:42.469
and I pray over them. In

00:01:42.479 --> 00:01:44.469
this dream, there was a

00:01:44.479 --> 00:01:47.990
circle of people surrounding a person in

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.149
the middle. The person in the

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:55.429
middle was a man whose face

00:01:55.429 --> 00:01:55.439
was

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:58.709
shaded out, like it was

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:00.469
blurry,

00:02:00.469 --> 00:02:00.479
so

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:03.550
I could not see his face.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:06.709
But this person was completely

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:11.390
gold, beautiful translucent gold,

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:14.750
and he was speaking to the elders around

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:19.110
this circle. I heard these

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:22.470
men and women say, 'This will make us

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:27.190
billions for the end-time harvest. This

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:30.470
is a genius, amazing idea. This is

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:32.229
brilliant.'I

00:02:32.239 --> 00:02:35.670
was a younger kid

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:39.030
outside the circle and I started

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:42.589
jumping up and down because, as the man

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:45.710
was speaking, I could not hear him

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:45.720
clearly.

00:02:45.720 --> 00:02:48.430
I was screaming as loud as I

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:50.710
could, 'Please tell me! I

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:52.229
want to know what y'all are talking

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:55.110
about!'I

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.229
started trying to

00:02:57.239 --> 00:02:59.110
reach up on those men's shoulders and

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:02.229
pull myself up to be able to hear.

00:03:02.239 --> 00:03:04.030
The man with no face, who was

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:06.350
completely translucent—this beautiful gold and

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:08.830
shining with glory—leaned over and

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:11.509
said, 'I have not forgotten you;

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:12.949
I will tell you

00:03:12.949 --> 00:03:12.959
too.'And

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:16.070
he spoke the

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:19.630
name of a company to

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:23.430
me, a

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:25.550
crypto.

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:29.470
He spoke this crypto name to

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:32.869
me, a company name.

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:39.710
I was so excited to go and tell my

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:41.110
friends and

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:45.589
family whoever I could about this

00:03:45.599 --> 00:03:49.110
name. I ran as fast as I could and I

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:51.670
grew up a little bit. I was no longer

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:53.750
a little child;

00:03:53.750 --> 00:03:53.760
I

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:56.789
became

00:03:56.799 --> 00:04:01.149
more mature in the dream. I

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:03.830
went, and all of a sudden, an angel

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:07.229
appeared before me. This angel

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:10.429
had the most beautiful blue sapphire

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:13.470
eyes I’ve ever seen, with

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:13.480
snow-white

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:15.750
skin and beautiful

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.229
blond-looking

00:04:18.239 --> 00:04:20.710
hair with fig

00:04:20.710 --> 00:04:20.720
leaves and

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.469
stuff in his hair.

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:25.350
He had a white

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:28.830
robe on with golden lace

00:04:28.830 --> 00:04:28.840
and

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:32.230
tassels

00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:32.240
on

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:34.230
this

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.510
garment. The

00:04:37.520 --> 00:04:40.029
angel followed me around. I

00:04:40.039 --> 00:04:41.710
believe it was my angel, but I’m not sure

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:44.070
who it was,

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:46.230
actually.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:50.870
I walked up to this house and

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:52.749
I could see the beautiful bricks;

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:54.310
it was a two-story

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:56.430
home with a courtyard. It was

00:04:56.440 --> 00:04:59.230
gorgeous. In

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:02.790
my front yard, I had an Aston Martin

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:07.670
sports car, a beautiful deep

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:11.350
blue convertible with

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:16.270
nice silver wheels. There

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:20.430
was snow falling outside. I

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:22.990
was yelling to

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.830
people, but they could not hear me. I was

00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:25.840
telling

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:28.670
people before I went to the

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:30.950
car, but

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:33.110
they weren't hearing me. I was

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.790
like, 'Hello, hello! Do you hear what

00:05:35.790 --> 00:05:35.800
I’m

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:38.590
saying? I’m trying to tell you a name!

00:05:38.590 --> 00:05:38.600
I’m

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.749
trying to tell you what’s

00:05:40.749 --> 00:05:40.759
coming!'But

00:05:40.759 --> 00:05:43.230
they could not hear what I was

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:46.390
saying. It was like I was

00:05:50.039 --> 00:05:53.510
transparent. The angel told me, 'Hush now,'and put

00:05:53.510 --> 00:05:53.520
his fingers

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:56.590
on my lips.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:59.150
He said, 'Hush now. They are

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:02.510
not dead to self.

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:04.550
They cannot hear what you're trying

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:06.830
to tell them; they don't have ears to

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:09.670
hear.'I

00:06:09.680 --> 00:06:12.110
said, 'But I’ve got to warn them!

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:13.350
I love them! I’ve got to warn

00:06:13.350 --> 00:06:13.360
them!'He

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:17.029
goes, 'I know your heart. Hush now. They

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:20.790
don't hear it.'I ran out to the car

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:24.070
and I tried to breathe on the glass

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:28.029
with a mist

00:06:28.029 --> 00:06:28.039
because

00:06:28.039 --> 00:06:30.309
it was cold outside. It created a

00:06:30.319 --> 00:06:33.110
fog on the glass, and I tried to write the

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:38.390
name of the thing on the glass.

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:41.909
The angel

00:06:41.919 --> 00:06:46.189
said, 'Hush now, hush now. They can't hear

00:06:46.199 --> 00:06:49.909
it. They're not dead to

00:06:49.909 --> 00:06:49.919
self.'I

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:53.749
was frustrated, and

00:06:53.759 --> 00:06:56.990
the angel said, 'Look at the

00:06:56.990 --> 00:06:57.000
holly

00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:01.070
berry

00:07:01.070 --> 00:07:01.080
bush.'I

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:03.510
had these bushes all in my

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:05.830
courtyard with berries on

00:07:05.830 --> 00:07:05.840
them.

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:08.710
He said, 'You will know the time of

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:11.430
when this will take place: when the

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:15.550
berries on the bush are turning

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:19.270
red. Notice the berries on the

00:07:19.270 --> 00:07:19.280
bush.'The

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:21.309
berries were turning a beautiful red

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:24.510
color and the snow was falling.

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:37.189
I ran upstairs and I had a

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:40.710
Christmas party going on in my home. I

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:42.749
saw the wreaths on the walls. It was

00:07:42.749 --> 00:07:42.759
beautiful—a

00:07:42.759 --> 00:07:45.510
rock home inside, and the

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:47.790
fireplace was going with fire

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:49.270
burning. I had a television above the fireplace and

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:55.990
the

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:57.390
news was

00:07:57.400 --> 00:08:01.510
on. I was trying to tell everybody in

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:03.230
that

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:06.029
party,

00:08:06.039 --> 00:08:08.230
'Hello!'but

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:10.189
they could not see me. They were

00:08:10.189 --> 00:08:10.199
all

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:13.950
celebrating. They had nice

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:17.110
sweaters on

00:08:17.110 --> 00:08:17.120
and

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:19.550
were celebrating that the

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:22.670
Iraqi dinar had

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:25.749
reinstated. All of them had great wealth

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:27.990
from this reinstatement.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:30.909
Now, this is not financial advice;

00:08:32.630 --> 00:08:32.640
I’m

00:08:35.479 --> 00:08:38.029
just telling you a

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:40.630
dream.

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:43.870
They were all celebrating the

00:08:43.880 --> 00:08:46.150
reinstatement of the Iraqi

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:48.670
dinar because it went up in

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:51.870
value. They were standing on a

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:55.870
beautiful, thick

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:01.750
Persian rug,

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:07.030
celebrating

00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:07.040
their

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:10.110
now windfall of

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:13.590
money. I was trying so hard to talk

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:18.110
to them.

00:09:21.880 --> 00:09:26.310
My wife was in the kitchen,

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.910
which

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:32.630
was beautiful and white—the cabinets, the

00:09:32.630 --> 00:09:32.640
countertops,

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:34.829
everything.

00:09:34.839 --> 00:09:37.790
In fact, it was glowing with

00:09:37.800 --> 00:09:41.870
glory inside this beautiful kitchen.

00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:44.630
She had trays in her hands trying to

00:09:44.640 --> 00:09:49.230
serve the people with beautiful white

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:52.389
china.

00:09:57.800 --> 00:10:00.710
She came out with a tray,

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:05.030
and at this time, I thought I

00:10:05.030 --> 00:10:05.040
would

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:08.310
try one more time to tell the

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:11.269
people. The angel stood by, and there

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:15.670
was a

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:37.030
copper pot that had

00:10:51.839 --> 00:10:57.030
ripples and dents in it. I tried to write the name of the company

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:57.040
again on this

00:10:57.040 --> 00:10:59.990
copper pot by breathing on

00:10:59.990 --> 00:11:00.000
it

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:03.550
to make a fog.

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:07.190
My

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.790
wife came out of the kitchen and she

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:10.670
said,

00:11:10.680 --> 00:11:14.550
'Look! Look at the writing on the copper

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:17.870
pot to warn the people!'because she could see

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:20.990
it.

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:26.949
Whenever she said that,

00:11:26.959 --> 00:11:30.550
the TV came on and said, 'Today we

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:34.590
had the largest crash we've ever seen of

00:11:34.600 --> 00:11:38.269
the dollar in

00:11:38.269 --> 00:11:38.279
history—like

00:11:38.279 --> 00:11:42.150
a

00:11:42.150 --> 00:11:42.160
1929-style

00:11:42.160 --> 00:11:44.269
crash.'It

00:11:44.279 --> 00:11:47.710
was so large you could see the

00:11:47.710 --> 00:11:47.720
Dow;

00:11:47.720 --> 00:11:50.389
everything

00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:54.629
was crashing: the dollar, the stock market.

00:11:54.639 --> 00:11:56.829
This was a

00:11:56.839 --> 00:11:59.829
worldwide huge event.

00:12:04.680 --> 00:12:07.949
The lady that was doing the news

00:12:07.949 --> 00:12:07.959
broadcast

00:12:07.959 --> 00:12:11.550
was very perplexed and upset; I could

00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:15.030
see it on her face.

00:12:15.040 --> 00:12:18.269
As the Dow Jones on the ticker

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:20.230
was just falling,

00:12:23.199 --> 00:12:28.590
all of a sudden, everybody in the

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:32.829
room that had a

00:12:32.829 --> 00:12:32.839
windfall

00:12:32.839 --> 00:12:35.269
with

00:12:35.279 --> 00:12:38.629
the dinar lost

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:40.629
everything. They were standing on the

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:41.629
Persian

00:12:41.639 --> 00:12:44.509
rug and they lost

00:12:44.509 --> 00:12:44.519
everything—it’s

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:45.829
like the rug was pulled out from

00:12:45.839 --> 00:12:47.189
underneath

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:50.550
them. They were weeping on the

00:12:50.560 --> 00:12:53.310
rug. They didn't see what was on the

00:12:53.320 --> 00:12:56.629
copper pot before it was too late

00:12:56.639 --> 00:13:00.310
because the copper pot was stable.

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:03.430
What was on the copper pot

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:04.430
was

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:07.670
a

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:10.350
place of refuge.

00:13:11.839 --> 00:13:15.590
Everything else changed, but the

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:18.189
copper pot was the investment that kept

00:13:18.199 --> 00:13:19.509
everybody

00:13:19.519 --> 00:13:22.750
safe. But you didn't see it or hear it

00:13:22.760 --> 00:13:25.310
until you were dead to self.

00:13:29.880 --> 00:13:33.269
It was a warning from the Lord

00:13:33.279 --> 00:13:35.710
about future things that will take

00:13:35.720 --> 00:13:38.629
place, that you will have to be in sync

00:13:38.639 --> 00:13:40.750
with

00:13:40.760 --> 00:13:44.110
him step by step, like a soldier

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:51.749
following the voice of the Lord.

00:13:52.880 --> 00:13:56.629
You cannot be

00:13:56.639 --> 00:14:00.470
asleep and alive to self

00:14:00.470 --> 00:14:00.480
and

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:02.509
be able to hear him for

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:03.910
what's coming.

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:08.949
I heard him back in

00:14:08.959 --> 00:14:13.350
2023, but I haven't heard him

00:14:13.360 --> 00:14:17.550
since. It takes a steady

00:14:17.550 --> 00:14:17.560
beat

00:14:17.560 --> 00:14:18.310
of a

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:20.710
drum following the voice of the Lord on

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:23.230
a day-to-day basis.

00:14:27.360 --> 00:14:29.470
The

00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:32.350
Lord said to me, 'Brandon, I'm giving more

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:34.629
time. What are you going to do with

00:14:34.629 --> 00:14:34.639
these

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:35.870
next four

00:14:35.880 --> 00:14:38.269
years? What are you going to do with this

00:14:40.590 --> 00:14:40.600
harvest?'He

00:14:43.959 --> 00:14:47.069
said the prayers of my

00:14:47.079 --> 00:14:49.670
saints, because

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.629
if my people who are

00:14:51.639 --> 00:14:53.350
called by my name will humble themselves

00:14:53.360 --> 00:14:56.350
and pray,

00:14:56.360 --> 00:14:58.030
then he would hear from heaven and

00:14:58.040 --> 00:15:01.030
heal our land. He's given us a

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:05.470
window, folks. What was going to happen in

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:07.590
2025

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:12.150
has been

00:15:12.160 --> 00:15:14.829
pushed

00:15:14.839 --> 00:15:18.389
back because of the prayers

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:23.030
of the righteous.

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:27.069
Do we have a window for blessing?

00:15:27.079 --> 00:15:30.509
I told you we would see a great

